	<h1 class="title">游泳池里，黑白运动泳装也可以很出彩</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/112309/small/112309.png?1431932479" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Coolhunting CH Editors</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-20 10:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9618/medium/9618.jpg?1436675377" alt="" />			
	</div>
